{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-compound-finals/task-31","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":["<p>Slušao sam zvuk i vežbao izgovor kombinacija završnih glasova i slogova.</p>"],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"zh-a1-learn-compound-finals","challengeType":24,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Za izgovaranje <span class=\"highlighted-text\">uai</span>, počinjete sa jezikom podignutim i blizu tvrdog nepca za <span class=\"highlighted-text\">u</span>, zatim se lako pomera na položaj <span class=\"highlighted-text\">a</span>, a na kraju u položaj <span class=\"highlighted-text\">i</span>. Prijelaz treba da bude glatok, bez prekida između tri zvuka.</p>\n<p>Kada <span class=\"highlighted-text\">uai</span> se spaja sa početnim konsonantima, dobija slogove kao <span class=\"highlighted-text\">kuai</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">guai</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">huai</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">chuai</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">shuai</span>.</p>\n<p>Pokušajte da izgovorite ove slogove, a zatim koristite <span class=\"highlighted-text\">guai</span> u različitim tonomima kao primer.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Pinyin</th>\n<th>Herufi</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">guāi</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">乖</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">guǎi</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">拐</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">guài</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">怪</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"Chinese Curriculum","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-compound-finals/task-31"},"questions":[],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company2-center.png","charact